title: 12 Monkeys Season 1 - 2 Complete x264
description:
Syfy has recreated Terry Gilliam's 1995 film 12 Monkeys as a television series.

By the year 2043, the human race is all but extinct. A devastating virus has ravaged the population, killing over 7 billion people. Those who have survived are either hiding underground or fighting each other for the few resources that can still be found.

Realizing that humanity's only chance to survive is to stop the epidemic before it begins, a small group of scientists attempts to pinpoint the plague's origin through fragments of old media. Then, making use of a somewhat imprecise time-travel technology that was being developed before the outbreak, they send convict James Cole more than 25 years into the past to stop the infection from being unleashed upon the world.
